    <!--
      To add a new release:

      1. Build and archive in Xcode (Product > Archive > Distribute > Direct Distribution)
      2. Zip the .app:
           zip -r -y Jukebox-X.Y.Z.zip Jukebox.app
      3. Sign the zip:
           find ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/DerivedData -name "sign_update" -path "*/Sparkle*" 2>/dev/null
           /path/to/sign_update Jukebox-X.Y.Z.zip
         This prints: sparkle:edSignature="..." length="..."
      4. Create a GitHub Release (tag: vX.Y.Z), upload Jukebox-X.Y.Z.zip
      5. Add an <item> below with the signature, length, and GitHub Release asset URL
      6. Commit and push docs/appcast.xml to main
    -->
